Package cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.util

Utilities for JCOP.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
JcopRandom JcopRandom is wrapper around Random such that it removes the necessity to create lots of new Random() objects and it allows predictable behavior of whole application.
JcopRandomTest Tests proper behavior of JcopRandom utility.
PreciseTime This class is used to get variable times (CPU, System, User) in variable precision (miliseconds, nanoseconds)
PreciseTimestamp Holds all time information about one moment.
 

Package cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.util Description

Utilities for JCOP. Contains utilities such as precise time used to measure CPU/User/System time in benchmarks.
